  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects actively meeting the symptomatic criteria for CRS as defined by the Taskforce
             on Rhinosinusitis but with physical and endoscopic examination that is within normal
             limits

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who are pregnant

          -  Subjects with a diagnosis of immune suppression or suspicion of malignancy that may be
             affecting the nose/paranasal sinuses

          -  Subjects who have had prior sinus surgery or who have been previously treated with a
             &gt;3 week course of broad spectrum antibiotics for CRS
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
